channel.title: Logging On Problem
channel.description:
I have recently re-opened a server that I worked on and it was a huge success before. I have just modified it and I tried to log in my account. It went to the black screen that it shows when you log in. Then, it auto-logged out. I then tried to log in again and it said I was already logged in.
I was using TestScape source and I would really appreciate it if someone can help me. [br][size=1]Posted at: December 05, 2006, 03:11:32 PM[/size][hr] Please help.[br][size=1]Posted at: December 05, 2006, 03:31:14 PM[/size][hr] Please
